Cabella

01:28:55.112 --> 01:29:00.333
“Litany for the doom of Materasura”

01:29:01.136 --> 01:29:07.745
This is the world that feeds the Swiss
Banks’ Octopus.

01:29:07.996 --> 01:29:14.269
This is the world where too much
is not enough.

01:29:14.470 --> 01:29:19.466
This is the world where negativity
is a plus.

01:29:19.667 --> 01:29:27.390
This is the world where the saints
say: “Enough”.

01:29:43.549 --> 01:29:48.411
1. This is a world where 1.3 billion
people

01:29:48.612 --> 01:29:52.630
live on an income of less
than $1 a day

01:29:52.831 --> 01:29:57.676
and where the planet does not have
enough natural resources

01:29:57.877 --> 01:30:02.669
to sustain, at a worldwide scale,
the consumption pattern

01:30:02.870 --> 01:30:06.606
of Malaysia, leave alone America.

01:30:06.807 --> 01:30:08.620
PLEASE SHRI DURGA,

01:30:08.821 --> 01:30:13.445
DESTROY THE EVIL FORCES THAT
MATERIALISM CREATED.

01:30:13.646 --> 01:30:18.279
Om Twameva Sakshat

01:30:18.480 --> 01:30:26.028
Shri Durga Namoh Namaha.

01:30:26.229 --> 01:30:29.748
2. This is a world where ten per cent
of world trade

01:30:29.949 --> 01:30:35.130
is generated by drugs and narco-traffics,
or US$100 billion

01:30:35.331 --> 01:30:39.287
represents the amount that yearly
poisons mankind,

01:30:39.488 --> 01:30:42.451
while money laundering in Switzerland
and elsewhere

01:30:42.659 --> 01:30:45.083
has become a most prosperous
activity,

01:30:45.284 --> 01:30:48.911
reaching all levels of society.

01:30:49.112 --> 01:30:52.271
PLEASE SHRI RAKTABIJA VINASHINI,

01:30:52.472 --> 01:30:56.656
DESTROY THE EVIL FORCES THAT
MATERIALISM CREATED.

01:30:56.857 --> 01:31:01.776
Om Twameva Sakshat

01:31:01.977 --> 01:31:11.568
Shri Raktabija Vinashini
Namoh Namaha.

01:31:11.769 --> 01:31:15.636
3. This is a world where Wall Street
sucks the wealth

01:31:15.837 --> 01:31:19.253
from the working middle class
to bestow it upon the rich

01:31:19.454 --> 01:31:23.691
and where Walt Disney makes you
forget all about it.

01:31:23.892 --> 01:31:26.472
PLEASE SHRI KATYAYANI,

01:31:26.673 --> 01:31:30.860
DESTROY THE EVIL FORCES THAT
MATERIALISM CREATED.

01:31:31.061 --> 01:31:35.798
Om Twameva Sakshat

01:31:35.999 --> 01:31:45.587
Shri Katyayani Namoh Namaha.

01:31:45.788 --> 01:31:51.525
4. This is a world where an Egyptian
eats at MacDonalds in Cairo

01:31:51.726 --> 01:31:57.177
and a Chinese at Pizza Hut in Beijing,
because modern consumerism

01:31:57.378 --> 01:32:02.092
expresses the lowest common
denominator of world culture

01:32:02.293 --> 01:32:07.865
