values and traditions.

01:32:08.066 --> 01:32:10.895
PLEASE SHRI SHAKAMBARI,

01:32:11.096 --> 01:32:15.208
DESTROY THE EVIL FORCES THAT
MATERIALISM CREATED.

01:32:15.409 --> 01:32:19.864
Om Twameva Sakshat

01:32:20.065 --> 01:32:27.694
Shri Shakambari Namoh Namaha.

01:32:27.895 --> 01:32:32.104
5. The new multinational entities are
experimenting with new forms

01:32:32.305 --> 01:32:37.153
of dictatorship, setting their production
sites in the developing world,

01:32:37.354 --> 01:32:40.591
reducing to slavery a subdued
working class

01:32:40.792 --> 01:32:45.145
