of productivity gains.

01:32:45.346 --> 01:32:47.473
PLEASE SHRI RAKSHAKARI,

01:32:47.674 --> 01:32:51.731
DESTROY THE EVIL FORCES THAT
MATERIALISM CREATED.

01:32:51.932 --> 01:32:56.286
Om Twameva Sakshat

01:32:56.487 --> 01:33:04.341
Shri Rakshakari Namoh Namaha.

01:33:04.612 --> 01:33:09.708
6. The globalization of production and
services allow a few global players

01:33:09.939 --> 01:33:13.762
