Om Twameva Sakshat

01:33:28.160 --> 01:33:37.475
Shri Bhimadevi Namoh Namaha.

01:33:37.676 --> 01:33:42.131
7. Vast restructuration endeavours
are progressively leading

01:33:42.332 --> 01:33:46.485
to the eradication of small and
medium-sized enterprises

01:33:46.686 --> 01:33:53.095
for the benefit of gigantic corporations
operating on a worldwide scale.

01:33:53.296 --> 01:33:54.859
PLEASE SHRI CHANDIKA,

01:33:55.060 --> 01:33:59.862
DESTROY THE EVIL FORCES THAT
MATERIALISM CREATED.

01:34:00.063 --> 01:34:04.749
Om Twameva Sakshat

01:34:04.950 --> 01:34:12.904
Shri Chandika Namoh Namaha.

01:34:13.105 --> 01:34:18.345
8. The gradual concentration of liquid
wealth in the hands of the super rich

01:34:18.546 --> 01:34:23.288
is marginalizing national sovereignty
and its elected officials,

01:34:23.489 --> 01:34:28.134
and is imposing a titanic dimension
to the ruler-ship of money.

01:34:28.335 --> 01:34:30.122
PLEASE SHRI RAKSHASAGNI,

01:34:30.323 --> 01:34:33.947
DESTROY THE EVIL FORCES THAT
MATERIALISM CREATED.

01:34:34.148 --> 01:34:39.041
Om Twameva Sakshat

01:34:39.242 --> 01:34:47.399
Shri Rakshasagni Namoh Namaha.

01:34:47.600 --> 01:34:50.759
9. Greed raised to the power 108

01:34:50.960 --> 01:34:54.374
means the pauperization of the world’s
middle class

01:34:54.590 --> 01:34:58.612
and outrageous wealth for
the remaining 10%.

01:34:58.813 --> 01:35:01.450
PLEASE SHRI DAITYENDRA MARDINI,

01:35:01.651 --> 01:35:06.040
DESTROY THE EVIL FORCES THAT
MATERIALISM CREATED.

01:35:06.241 --> 01:35:10.664
Om Twameva Sakshat

01:35:10.865 --> 01:35:21.794
Shri Daityendra Mardini Namoh Namaha.

01:35:21.995 --> 01:35:26.864
10. The systematic elimination
of alternative economic solutions,

01:35:27.072 --> 01:35:33.025
unequal trade and financial manipulations
are challenging

01:35:33.227 --> 01:35:37.614
the equitable distribution of wealth
among the population of the world.

01:35:37.815 --> 01:35:39.601
PLEASE SHRI VAJRINI,

01:35:39.802 --> 01:35:43.091
DESTROY THE EVIL FORCES THAT
MATERIALISM CREATED.

01:35:43.292 --> 01:35:48.324
Om Twameva Sakshat

01:35:48.525 --> 01:35:55.633
Shri Vajrini Namoh Namaha.

01:35:55.834 --> 01:36:00.359
11. The deregulation of the financial
markets has opened wide the gates

01:36:00.560 --> 01:36:06.020
